title: It Ain't Over 'Til It's OVER
body_text:
DODGEBALL 135 Announcement!
For the first time in mid-season main event history, the 2007
RIVALRY of the Year
WALL vs. ALL
takes center stage! This will be the sixth meeting between the two factions and chances are, it'll be the biggest clash yet. WALL currently leads this heated series 3 to 2.
WALL vs. ALL History
DODGEBALL 93
..
DODGEBALL 97
..
DODGEBALL 107
..
DODGEBALL CX3
..
DODGEBALL CXX7
WOLF vs. JUAN Breaking News!
Beginning at DODGEBALL 135 and continuing for the next five weeks, DODGEBALL CXL headliners
Justin Wolf
and
Juan Londono
will be forced to compete
against
each other regardless of captains, stipulations, gametypes, etc. Talk about pouring a little gasoline onto this firey feud!
body_html:
DODGEBALL 135 Announcement!
For the first time in mid-season main event history, the 2007 RIVALRY of the Year WALL vs. ALL takes center stage! This will be the sixth meeting between the two factions and chances are, it'll be the biggest clash yet. WALL currently leads this heated series 3 to 2.

WALL vs. ALL History
DODGEBALL 93 .. DODGEBALL 97 .. DODGEBALL 107 .. DODGEBALL CX3 .. DODGEBALL CXX7


WOLF vs. JUAN Breaking News!
Beginning at DODGEBALL 135 and continuing for the next five weeks, DODGEBALL CXL headliners Justin Wolf and Juan Londono will be forced to compete against each other regardless of captains, stipulations, gametypes, etc. Talk about pouring a little gasoline onto this firey feud!
